    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-8014-bb94-dfd1635515f4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "This is nastro , showcasing what can u do to your notion pages with ",
            "href": null
          },
          {
            "text": "nastro",
            "href": "http://nastro.xyz/"
          },
          {
            "text": ". so seat back , relax ,and chill. ",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-80cc-978d-fde28e16e9f0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "Thing u can do with nastro , customize theme , literally u can customize everything in nastro , from background colors , notion button color to text selection.",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-8068-b7ae-fa2006db54fd",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "U can do seo , that for free , yes this is not a bait , notion charges for it , but with nastro u can do it easily and u can also add google analytics that is also free. ",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-80d6-8824-ea3a462fedf3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "Nastro , provide some custom themes , and  templates .",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-80a7-bb8f-c07f1c6cf901",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "content": {
        "level": 2,
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "why nastro exist ?",
            "href": null
          }
