      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "nastro can help to make your fist website , that represent truly you , ",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-801e-bc25-d6c8cc766168",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "it can help you to publish blog on your name , (eliza.nastro.xyz)",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "33785bde-2593-80b2-ab69-ce4b94acb450",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "it can help you to validate your idea without wasting thousands on just validations. (you can literally make small ecommerce website.",
